---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HeartStrings Connect | Private-Test Digital Companion"
  description="HeartStrings Connect is in private Android development. Screenshots show current UI surfaces. Not available in any public app store."
  keywords="HeartStrings Connect, private beta, digital companion, ByteLite LLC"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="app-hero">
    <div class="container app-hero-inner">
      <div class="app-hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">HeartStrings Connect</p>
        <h1>The private-test digital companion for the HeartStrings ecosystem.</h1>
        <p class="app-hero-sub">
          HeartStrings Connect is the private companion layer for the ecosystem &mdash; rooms, prompts,
          consent flows, date planning, and future social features. Building on Android, not in any
          app store; the screens below are current private-test UI.
        </p>
        <img src="/heartstrings-app/app-icon.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect icon" width="130" height="130" style="width:130px;height:130px;margin-top:1.5rem;display:block;border-radius:24px;" loading="lazy" />
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:1.75rem;">
          <span class="badge badge-private">Private beta development</span>
          <span style="font-size:.875rem;color:#555e7a;">No public app store listing</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.875rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2rem;">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Beta Interest</a>
          <a href="/status" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" style="align-self:center;">View Status</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="app-hero-visual">
        <div class="phone-frame">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/screenshots/28_discover_with_match.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Connect — Discover screen showing a match card"
            class="phone-img"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="hero-img-label">Current screen — Discover</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What makes it different -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Makes It Different</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Built around three things most dating apps ignore.</h2>
      <p class="ss-intro" style="max-width:680px;">
        Most apps show you an endless stream of faces and let you swipe. HeartStrings Connect is
        built around whether two people genuinely fit, keeping your private answers actually
        private, and watching out for your safety when you go meet someone in real life.
      </p>

      <div class="deep-list">
        <article class="deep-item">
          <div class="deep-num">01</div>
          <div class="deep-body">
            <h3>Matching that goes deeper than a swipe</h3>
            <p>
              A compatibility questionnaire that starts short &mdash; about 75 questions &mdash; and
              can go as deep as you want, all the way up to hundreds of questions covering your
              values, how you handle emotions, your lifestyle, your plans for the future, and your
              intimacy preferences. HeartStrings uses your answers to surface people you are
              genuinely compatible with.
            </p>
            <ul class="deep-points">
              <li>Respects your dealbreakers both ways: if something is a hard no, it won&rsquo;t match you with someone who fails it &mdash; and it won&rsquo;t match you to someone whose hard no is you.</li>
              <li>Figures out your love language, and your zodiac sign from your birthday.</li>
              <li>Gives you a daily horoscope.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deep-item">
          <div class="deep-num">02</div>
          <div class="deep-body">
            <h3>Private answers protected by real cryptography</h3>
            <p>
              When you finish the survey, your answers are mathematically split into two scrambled
              halves that are sent to two separate places &mdash; and neither half means anything on
              its own. Even HeartStrings&rsquo; own servers can&rsquo;t read what you actually
              answered, so your most personal information never sits anywhere readable.
            </p>
            <ul class="deep-points">
              <li>Most apps say &ldquo;we protect your data.&rdquo; This one is built so it literally can&rsquo;t see it.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deep-item">
          <div class="deep-num">03</div>
          <div class="deep-body">
            <h3>Safety treated as a core feature, not an afterthought</h3>
            <p>
              Meeting a stranger in person is the risky part of online dating, so before or during a
              date you can share your live location with people you trust and drop check-in pins on a
              real map as the night goes &mdash; &ldquo;I&rsquo;m leaving now,&rdquo; &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve
              arrived,&rdquo; &ldquo;I&rsquo;m back at my car&rdquo; &mdash; so your trusted contacts
              know you&rsquo;re okay.
            </p>
            <ul class="deep-points">
              <li>Set up emergency contacts, plus a spoken safety phrase you can say if you ever feel unsafe.</li>
              <li>Honest by design: it tells you plainly when it&rsquo;s contacting someone.</li>
              <li>It never pretends to be the police or 911, and it never secretly records anyone.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current status -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="app-status-box">
        <h3 style="color:#e4e7f2;margin-bottom:1rem;">Current Status</h3>
        <div class="app-status-grid">
          <div class="app-status-item">
            <span class="badge badge-private">Private test builds</span>
            <p>Used for internal development validation. Not for public distribution.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-status-item">
            <span class="badge badge-none">No public app store listing</span>
            <p>Not available on Google Play, Apple App Store, or any third-party marketplace.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-status-item">
            <span class="badge badge-active">Active development</span>
            <p>UI surfaces, onboarding, and companion features are actively under development.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-status-item">
            <span class="badge badge-planned">Beta program planned</span>
            <p>A limited private beta program is planned. Contact to express interest.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current UI Surfaces -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Current UI Surfaces</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">What the app looks like today.</h2>
      <p class="ss-intro">Screenshots from private Android test builds. Current development surfaces — not final production UI.</p>
      <div class="ss-grid-3">

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/01_login.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — login screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Authentication</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/06_discover_home.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — discover home" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Discover</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/06_matches.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — matches screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Matches</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/07_messages.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — messages screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Messages</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/08_profile.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — profile screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Profile</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/09_settings.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — settings screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Settings</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature Surfaces -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Feature Surfaces</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Additional screens in development.</h2>
      <p class="ss-intro">These feature areas have active UI. Not all workflows are complete or production-ready.</p>
      <div class="ss-grid-3">

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/15_safety_hub.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — safety hub" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-dev">In development</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Safety Hub</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/23_game_room.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — game room" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-dev">In development</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Game Room</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/16_date_hub.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — date hub" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-dev">In development</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Date Hub</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/14_match_detail.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — match detail" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-current">Current screen</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Match Detail</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/25_friendship_friends.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — friendship friends screen" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-dev">In development</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Friendship</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/17_photo_styles.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — photo styles" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-dev">In development</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">Photo Styles</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- More than matching -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">More Than Matching</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Getting to know someone, made playful.</h2>
      <p class="ss-intro">Once you&rsquo;ve matched, HeartStrings Connect is designed to be genuinely fun to use together &mdash; not just another inbox.</p>
      <div class="play-grid">
        <div class="play-card">
          <span class="play-kicker">Game Room</span>
          <h3>Play together</h3>
          <p>Games you can play with a match &mdash; from truth-or-dare and would-you-rather to chess and trivia &mdash; as a low-pressure way to get to know each other.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="play-card">
          <span class="play-kicker">Blind Date Roulette</span>
          <h3>Meet by chance</h3>
          <p>Jump into a pool and get spontaneously paired with someone, for when you&rsquo;d rather leave it to chance than keep scrolling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="play-card">
          <span class="play-kicker">AIya Companion</span>
          <h3>A friendly guide</h3>
          <p>AIya is designed to help and encourage you &mdash; never to trick you or pretend to be a real person. See the research preview below.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AIya Guide Preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">AIya Guide Interface</p>
      <span class="badge badge-research" style="margin-bottom:.75rem;display:inline-block;">Research Preview &mdash; Not Production AI</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Research preview — not a production AI system.</h2>
      <p style="max-width:640px;margin-top:.25rem;font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.8;">
        AIya is a research concept for a guided interface layer within the HeartStrings ecosystem.
        These screens are preview surfaces from private development.
      </p>
      <p style="max-width:640px;margin-top:.75rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-size:.875rem;color:#555e7a;">
        No live AI companion, automated matching system, or production guidance system is deployed.
        This is in-development research only.
      </p>
      <img src="/heartstrings-app/aiya-research-preview-card.png" alt="AIya Research Preview card — concept art, clearly labeled research preview, not a production AI system" style="width:100%;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:2.5rem;display:block;height:auto;border-radius:14px;" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="ss-grid-2-constrained">

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/05_ai_onboarding.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — AI onboarding flow" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-research">Research preview</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">AI Onboarding Flow</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ss-card">
          <img src="/heartstrings/screenshots/11_wingman_aiya.png" alt="HeartStrings Connect — AIya interface" class="ss-img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="ss-meta">
            <span class="ss-tag tag-research">Research preview</span>
            <p class="ss-caption">AIya Interface</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Principles -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Principles Built In On Purpose</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:.75rem;">Designed to do right by people.</h2>
      <p class="ss-intro" style="max-width:640px;">
        Underneath the features runs a set of principles the creator built in deliberately. The
        guiding idea: a good system should do the right thing because of how it&rsquo;s built, not
        because someone&rsquo;s watching &mdash; and kindness and protecting people should come first.
      </p>
      <div class="privacy-list">
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Doesn&rsquo;t sell your data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Doesn&rsquo;t use your private dating life to target ads.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>No manipulative tricks designed to keep you hooked.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Built to be honest: no fake matches, no fake urgency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Stance</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Privacy-first by design.</h2>
      <div class="privacy-list">
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Private test builds are not connected to advertising networks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>No personal data is sold or shared with third parties.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>A full app-specific privacy policy will be published before any public launch or broader beta release.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-item">
          <span class="privacy-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <p>Beta participants will be informed of any data handling specific to their testing role.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beta interest CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container cta-block">
      <h2>Interested in private beta?</h2>
      <p>The beta program is not yet open. Express interest and you will be contacted when slots become available.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Express Beta Interest</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Architecture note -->
  <section class="section-sm section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:.875rem;color:#4a5068;">
        AIya and deterministic guide interfaces are part of the broader research stack described on
        <a href="/architecture" style="color:#555e7a;">The Architecture</a> page.
        Not a production AI system.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>

/* Hero */
.app-hero {
  padding: 6rem 0 4.5rem;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% -5%, rgba(99,102,241,.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
}
.app-hero-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
  gap: 3rem;
  align-items: center;
}
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .app-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .app-hero-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
}
.app-hero-text h1 { max-width: 620px; }
.app-hero-sub { max-width: 520px; margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #7b829e; line-height: 1.75; }
.app-hero-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: .75rem; }
.phone-frame {
  max-width: 260px;
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid #24304a;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.55), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.03);
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #0d1120;
}
.phone-img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
.hero-img-label {
  font-size: .6875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #4a5068;
}

/* Status */
.app-status-box { background: #111828; border: 1px solid #1a2235; border-radius: .875rem; padding: 2rem; }
.app-status-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; }
@media (max-width: 640px) { .app-status-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.app-status-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.app-status-item p { font-size: .875rem; color: #7b829e; }

/* Screenshot section intro text */
.ss-intro {
  max-width: 580px;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  font-size: .9375rem;
  color: #555e7a;
}

/* Screenshot grids */
.ss-grid-3 {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) { .ss-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 480px)  { .ss-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.ss-grid-2-constrained {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  max-width: 520px;
}
@media (max-width: 480px) { .ss-grid-2-constrained { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* Screenshot card */
.ss-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.ss-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 1.25rem;
  border: 1px solid #1a2235;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  transition: box-shadow .2s, border-color .2s;
  background: #0d1120;
}
.ss-img:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.5); border-color: #24304a; }
.ss-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .25rem; }
.ss-tag {
  font-size: .6875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: .2rem .5rem;
  border-radius: .25rem;
  display: inline-block;
}
.tag-current  { background: rgba(52,211,153,.1);   color: #34d399; }
.tag-dev      { background: rgba(99,102,241,.12);  color: #818cf8; }
.tag-research { background: rgba(167,139,250,.12); color: #a78bfa; }
.ss-caption   { font-size: .875rem; color: #7b829e; }

/* Privacy */
.privacy-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
.privacy-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .875rem; }
.privacy-icon { font-size: 1rem; color: #34d399; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .125rem; }
.privacy-item p { font-size: 1rem; color: #a0a8c0; }

/* CTA */
.cta-block {
  background: #0d1120; border: 1px solid #1a2235; border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 3.5rem; text-align: center;
}
.cta-block h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.cta-block p { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: 1.0625rem; }

/* Deep-dive pillars */
.deep-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2.75rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
.deep-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: start; }
.deep-num {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #818cf8;
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  width: 2.75rem;
  height: 2.75rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border: 1px solid #24304a;
  border-radius: .75rem;
  background: #111828;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.deep-body h3 { color: #e4e7f2; margin-bottom: .625rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
.deep-body > p { color: #a0a8c0; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 640px; }
.deep-points { list-style: none; margin: 1rem 0 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.deep-points li { position: relative; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #7b829e; font-size: .9375rem; line-height: 1.65; }
.deep-points li::before { content: "\2192"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #818cf8; }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .deep-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: .875rem; } }

/* Play / companion cards */
.play-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
@media (max-width: 760px) { .play-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.play-card { background: #111828; border: 1px solid #1a2235; border-radius: .875rem; padding: 1.75rem; }
.play-kicker {
  font-size: .6875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: .1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #818cf8;
}
.play-card h3 { color: #e4e7f2; margin: .5rem 0 .625rem; font-size: 1.125rem; }
.play-card p { color: #7b829e; font-size: .9375rem; line-height: 1.7; }

</style>
